episodes.title: Trailer | The Cult of the Real Housewife | TLC
episodes.description:
Her story on The Real Housewives of Salt Lake City made her a TV star, but the reality is far more bizarre. #TheCultoftheRealHousewife unpacks the allegations surrounding Mary Cosby and her church. The explosive three-part docuseries premieres Thursday, Jan 1 at 8/7c.
